title: Crude suicide rate in Vietnam 2000 to 2015
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Crude suicide rate per 100,000 inhabitants, with a total of 4 data points. The chart has 2 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly positive which exists from 2015 to 2000.
In a similar manner, the next significant trend is slightly negative which exists from 2015 to 2015.
gold: This statistic shows the crude suicide rate in Vietnam from 2000 to 2015 . In 2015 , the crude suicide rate in Vietnam was approximately 7.4 deaths per 100,000 inhabitants .
